tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE water_conservation_campaign (
  campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(255),
  outreach_date DATE,
  num_participants INT,
  water_saved DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
	participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	program_id INT,
	participant_name VARCHAR(255),
	registration_date DATE,
	city VARCHAR(100)
);

CREATE TABLE outreach_programs (
    program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    program_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE NOT NULL,
    end_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE program_participants (
    participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT NOT NULL,
    participant_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    contact_email VARCHAR(50),
    registration_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE program_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    program_id INT NOT NULL,
    participant_id INT NOT NULL,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    feedback_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (program_id) REFERENCES outreach_programs(program_id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    FOREIGN KEY (participant_id) REFERENCES program_participants(participant_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE OutreachPrograms (
  program_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_name VARCHAR(255),
  outreach_type VARCHAR(50),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Participants (
  participant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(255),
  contact_number VARCHAR(20),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  address VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE ProgramFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id INT,
  participant_id INT,
  rating INT,
  feedback_text TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Sessions (
  session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id INT,
  session_date DATE,
  session_time TIME,
  location VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE Metrics (
  metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  program_id INT,
  participants_reached INT,
  water_saved_liters INT,
  trees_planted INT
);
